l放隔壁（摔"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/14/02/140247.jpg","floor":"#3-3","id":"1247720","time":"2017-6-11 20:59","userId":"me476210180","userName":"476210180","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">LunarShaddow</span> 说: 一开始部署的时候没考虑好吧……CentOS 6好多东西都得自己装了……<br>其实7也要，所以可以考虑自己编译一套openssl放隔壁（摔</q></div>所有不能被包管理器管理的软件都是隐患【滑稽"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/05/37/53750.jpg","floor":"#3-4","id":"1247729","time":"2017-6-11 21:08","userId":"spdf","userName":"一树小草","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">476210180</span> 说: 1.0.1支持NPN实现HTTP2<br>然后俺也开始想要不要换系统了……关键是已经部署了不少业务了……</q></div>话说楼主的Debian 8哪里搞到的OpenSSL 1.0.2（为啥我的没有）"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/20/82/208208.jpg","floor":"#3-5","id":"1247851","time":"2017-6-11 22:50","userId":"aflyhorse","userName":"LunarShaddow🌙","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">476210180</span> 说: 所有不能被包管理器管理的软件都是隐患【滑稽</q></div>可以考虑 gentoo prefix （阴险"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/20/82/208208.jpg","floor":"#3-6","id":"1247855","time":"2017-6-11 22:52","userId":"aflyhorse","userName":"LunarShaddow🌙","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">一树小草</span> 说: 话说楼主的Debian 8哪里搞到的OpenSSL 1.0.2（为啥我的没有）</q></div>目前好像是 1.0.1t 来着"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/14/02/140247.jpg","floor":"#3-7","id":"1248044","time":"2017-6-12 08:02","userId":"me476210180","userName":"476210180","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">一树小草</span> 说: 话说楼主的Debian 8哪里搞到的OpenSSL 1.0.2（为啥我的没有）</q></div>去backports或者experimental里就有啦<br>我甚至用了stretch里的1.1.0e"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/05/37/53750.jpg","floor":"#3-8","id":"1248118","time":"2017-6-12 10:56","userId":"spdf","userName":"一树小草","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">476210180</span> 说: 去backports或者experimental里就有啦<br>我甚至用了stretch里的1.1.0e</q></div>我印象中backports里面没有openssl 和nginx（当然我后来已经改用openSUSE了"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/14/02/140247.jpg","floor":"#3-9","id":"1248135","time":"2017-6-12 11:48","userId":"me476210180","userName":"476210180","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">一树小草</span> 说: 我印象中backports里面没有openssl 和nginx（当然我后来已经改用openSUSE了</q></div>有啊<br>jessie-backports，nginx-full 1.10.3，libssl 1.0.2k"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/17/78/177820.jpg","floor":"#3-10","id":"1248184","time":"2017-6-12 13:49","userId":"franklinyu","userName":"Franklin Yu","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">一树小草</span> 说: 我印象中backports里面没有openssl 和nginx（当然我后来已经改用openSUSE了</q></div><a href=\"https://packages.debian.org/jessie-backports/openssl\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">https://packages.debian.org/jessie-backports/openssl</a>"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/05/37/53750.jpg","floor":"#3-11","id":"1248520","time":"2017-6-12 23:57","userId":"spdf","userName":"一树小草","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">476210180</span> 说: 有啊<br>jessie-backports，nginx-full 1.10.3，libssl 1.0.2k</q></div>真的额，看了一下是去年8月份添加的，一直都思维定视了。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/05/37/53750.jpg","floor":"#3-12","id":"1248521","time":"2017-6-12 23:57","userId":"spdf","userName":"一树小草","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Franklin Yu</span> 说: https://packages.debian.org/jessie-backports/openssl</q></div>额，那我换个腿的openSUSE"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/17/78/177820.jpg","floor":"#3-13","id":"1248549","time":"2017-6-13 02:04","userId":"franklinyu","userName":"Franklin Yu","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">一树小草</span> 说: 额，那我换个腿的openSUSE</q></div><img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/17/78/177820.jpg","floor":"#3-14","id":"1248552","time":"2017-6-13 02:34","userId":"franklinyu","userName":"Franklin Yu","userSign":"","message":"然而 7 也只有 1.0.1e：<a href=\"http://centos-packages.com/7/package/openssl/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">http://centos-packages.com/7/package/openssl/</a>"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/20/82/208208.jpg","floor":"#3-15","id":"1248804","time":"2017-6-13 12:06","userId":"aflyhorse","userName":"LunarShaddow🌙","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Franklin Yu</span> 说: 然而 7 也只有 1.0.1e：http://centos-packages.com/7/package/openssl/</q></div>7毕竟是14年的货<br>按发行速度感觉8明年就要出了"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/14/02/140247.jpg","floor":"#3-16","id":"1249105","time":"2017-6-13 22:28","userId":"me476210180","userName":"476210180","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">一树小草</span> 说: 额，那我换个腿的openSUSE</q></div>2333"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/17/78/177820.jpg","floor":"#3-17","id":"1250137","time":"2017-6-16 04:27","userId":"franklinyu","userName":"Franklin Yu","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">476210180</span> 说: 去backports或者experimental里就有啦<br>我甚至用了stretch里的1.1.0e</q></div>stretch 是不是今年還是明年要釋出？"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/19/95/199502.jpg","floor":"#4","id":"1248560","time":"2017-6-13 03:21","userId":"wjself","userName":"灰灰","userSign":"(もうぅ！プラチナむかつく！)","message":"不考虑用下 openssl 1.1.1 么 XD<br>既然上了h2 为何不一起把Tls 1.3也一起上了呢  <img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/14/02/140247.jpg","floor":"#4-1","id":"1249104","time":"2017-6-13 22:28","userId":"me476210180","userName":"476210180","userSign":"","message":"妈的我也好想上TLS 1.3啊，但是没有OpenSSL 1.1.1的包，Debian就算stretch也才到1.1.0f"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/19/95/199502.jpg","floor":"#4-2","id":"1249138","time":"2017-6-13 23:03","userId":"wjself","userName":"灰灰","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">476210180</span> 说: 妈的我也好想上TLS 1.3啊，但是没有OpenSSL 1.1.1的包，Debian就算stretch也才到1.1.0f</q></div>因为还没有tls1.3还在draft阶段，目前到draft20<br>openssl的话还在实现draft20<br>draft19的话<br><a href=\"https://github.com/openssl/openssl/tree/tls1.3-draft-19\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">https://github.com/openssl/openssl/tree/tls1.3-draft-19</a><br>要用tls1.3可以把这个拿去编译("},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/17/78/177820.jpg","floor":"#4-3","id":"1249245","time":"2017-6-14 03:20","userId":"franklinyu","userName":"Franklin Yu","userSign":"","message":"TLS 1.3 需要 nginx 支持麼"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/19/95/199502.jpg","floor":"#4-4","id":"1249547","time":"2017-6-14 16:45","userId":"wjself","userName":"灰灰","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Franklin Yu</span> 说: TLS 1.3 需要 nginx 支持麼</q></div>詳細要部署的話可以看下這個博文 <a href=\"https://www.isthnew.com/openssl-dev-tls1_3-support/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">https://www.isthnew.com/openssl-dev-tls1_3-support/</a>"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/14/02/140247.jpg","floor":"#4-5","id":"1249630","time":"2017-6-14 18:45","userId":"me476210180","userName":"476210180","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Franklin Yu</span> 说: TLS 1.3 需要 nginx 支持麼</q></div>nginx最新mainline版本已经支持了，有OpenSSL 1.1.1就行。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/17/78/177820.jpg","floor":"#4-6","id":"1249897","time":"2017-6-15 13:33","userId":"franklinyu","userName":"Franklin Yu","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">灰灰</span> 说: 詳細要部署的話可以看下這個博文 https://www.isthnew.com/openssl-dev-tls1_3-support/</q></div>並不布署…… 畢竟 1.1.1 還沒正式釋出？"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/17/78/177820.jpg","floor":"#4-7","id":"1249898","time":"2017-6-15 13:36","userId":"franklinyu","userName":"Franklin Yu","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">476210180</span> 说: nginx最新mainline版本已经支持了，有OpenSSL 1.1.1就行。</q></div>要 mainline？上面那篇博客寫的是 1.11.10，現在 stable 已經 1.12 了……（不太瞭解 nginx 的分支）"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/19/95/199502.jpg","floor":"#4-8","id":"1249937","time":"2017-6-15 14:52","userId":"wjself","userName":"灰灰","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Franklin Yu</span> 说: 要 mainline？上面那篇博客寫的是 1.11.10，現在 stable 已經 1.12 了……（不太瞭解 nginx 的分支）</q></div>看了下changelog nginx在1.13.0開始支援 ssl_protocols 的 tlsv1.3參數<br>舊版本沒有這個參數，但是寫tlsv1.2也能用的意思XD"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/14/02/140247.jpg","floor":"#4-9","id":"1250006","time":"2017-6-15 20:38","userId":"me476210180","userName":"476210180","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Franklin Yu</span> 说: 要 mainline？上面那篇博客寫的是 1.11.10，現在 stable 已經 1.12 了……（不太瞭解 nginx 的分支）</q></div>这是<a href=\"https://nginx.org/en/CHANGES\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">nginx mainline的更新日志</a>，在1.13.0加入了TLS 1.3参数<br><div class=\"codeHighlight\"><pre>Changes with nginx 1.13.0                                        25 Apr 2017<br><br>    ....<br>    *) Feature: the \"TLSv1.3\" parameter of the \"ssl_protocols\" directive.<br>    ....<br></pre></div><br>从1.1.13(stable)支持TLS 1.2，所以说1.13.0以下的版本都最高到TLS 1.2。"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/17/78/177820.jpg","floor":"#5","id":"1250143","time":"2017-6-16 05:42","userId":"franklinyu","userName":"Franklin Yu","userSign":"(讓一切都自動化！)","message":"我一直想吐槽 OpenSSL 的版本系統…… 1.0.2 的意思其實是 1.2，1.1.0 其實是 2.0…… 反正 1.x.y 相當於 (x+1).y……","sub":[]}]